// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2568 — Mass File Rename (snatch)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 90373832-77a4-5714-8ee2-491577454a52

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
